Changes to vanilla PGPLOT v5.2.2 carried out
for the incorporation into the Tycho distribution:

* drivers.list:

- include the following drivers:
  NUDRIV 
  PSDRIF 1 2 3 4
  XWDRIV 1 2
  
- created install directory "PGPLOT/lib"

- added little script (make_pgplot_tycho.sh) to
  generate the PGPLOT makefile and set up
  environment files.

- using sys_linux config options; added generic
  option set 'tycho.conf.in' that is edited by
  make_pgplot_tycho, setting CC, FC and FFLAGS.

- added Makefile to control entire PGPLOT make
  process; make_pgplot_tycho.sh is called by this
  make file.



